sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant BookingService
    participant DynamoDB
    participant EventBridge
    participant NotificationService

    Client->>BookingService: POST /v1/bookings
    BookingService->>BookingService: Extract guestId from Cognito JWT
    BookingService->>DynamoDB: Save booking with status pending
    BookingService->>EventBridge: Publish booking.created
    EventBridge-->>NotificationService: Async notification event
    BookingService-->>Client: 201 Created